{"type":"message","id":"42544e01","parentId":"8931e825","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:53:50.391Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-03-21 13:53 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索以下行业的最新动态（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防/智慧城市\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n5. 企业数字化、智能安防、系统集成行业政策\n\n请搜索最新资讯，整理3-5条对道简网络（企业数字化解决方案、网络系统集成、智能安防与弱电工程、IT全周期运维服务）有参考价值的关键信息，输出格式：\n- 信息标题\n- 核心内容摘要\n- 对道简网络的参考意义\n\n只输出信息，不需要其他内容。"}],"timestamp":1774072430388}}
{"type":"message","id":"c52f258b","parentId":"42544e01","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:53:56.820Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The subagent task is to search for the latest industry news (March 2026) in:\n1. Enterprise digital transformation\n2. Smart security/smart city\n3. Network system integration\n4. IT operations services\n5. Industry policies for digital transformation, smart security, system integration\n\nI need to search for this information and compile 3-5 key pieces of information that are valuable for 道简网络 (Daojian Network - a company providing enterprise digital solutions, network system integration, smart security and weak current engineering, IT full-cycle operations services).\n\nLet me use the web search skill to find the latest information.","thinkingSignature":"3a79316a11366c240041223e79ab82084d6d6b9665012737ef250a13efcdcb6a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_os8sb4686f3u_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":166,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":31559,"totalTokens":31842,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.0001992,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0037870799999999995,"total":0.00402138}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774072430390}}
{"type":"message","id":"4976faa3","parentId":"c52f258b","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:53:56.826Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_os8sb4686f3u_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774072436823}}
{"type":"message","id":"79cab81c","parentId":"4976faa3","timestamp":"2026-03-21T05:54:00.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll use the web search command to search for the latest information in these industries. Let me search for multiple topics simultaneously.","thinkingSignature":"9a76b8307c656a8489844083c9225420522088d238824b94223579d282c2bf3b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hzxtxfs88f5k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026年3月 最新政策动态\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hzxtxfs88f5k_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 智慧城市 2026年3月 最新动态\" --output json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_hzxtxfs88f5k_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026年3月 行业动态\" --output json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":978,"output":168,"cacheRead":31379,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32525,"cost":{"input":0.0002934,"output":0.0002016,"cacheRead":0.00094137,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00143637}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774072436825}}
